description: Available at https://openstudionetwork.com/keezer - Geoffrey credits the great pianist Hank Jones as a major influence on his sound and style. Based on one of Hank's most beautiful harmonic concepts, these exercises will stretch your hands AND your brain! For people with smaller hands, there are modifications in the exercises and accompanying PDF. (Level: Intermediate/Advanced)
